My solution to this problem was to get rid of the /data folder (which contains the .txt file for local storage) each time the test finishes by adding:

'''bash
rmdir /s /q data 
'''
at the end of the runtest.bat file.

This allows you to continue testing your other features (apart from the save/load) in a predictable manner.


