</div>

Thanks for sharing! I found an alternative which works for me as well.

In Intellij, Go to Settings > Editor > Code Style > Java, select tab "Wrapping and Braces", scroll down the list to 'switch' statement, uncheck the option "Indent 'case' branches".

More information can be found here: https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/code-style-java.html#tabs-and-indents-tab
</panel>

