hi! the display of characters are dependent on the terminal doing the display. this means that although it does not display right on your windows machine, it actually displays properly on a device with a different OS (eg. Mac). I also faced that issue on my Windows but works fine on my Mac. Maybe [this article](https://www.baeldung.com/java-char-encoding) would help you better understand Java character encoding on Windows!
